item.summary: Fuse won't start with IBM java

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.

comments.comment:
Automated ldap tests were passing on #179 and they're failing on #183 and #185 ibm jdk.

Teste were re-run with #179 and ibm jdk 8 on RHEL7 and it's working -> problem should be in fuse, not in some update of ibm jdk or another enviroment chagne.
Automated ldap tests are passing again with build 189 on both ibm1.8 and ibm1.7 (and OpenJDK and Oracle JDK didn't break
